        B.S. in <strong><i>Electrical Engineering</i></strong>
      </li>
      <li>
        Double Major in <strong><i>Computer Science</i></strong>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong><i>Program of Finance</i></strong> 
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Collapse>

  <Collapse title='National Taiwan University (2022 - 2023)'>
    <ul>
      <li>
        B.S. in <strong><i>Bioenvironmental Systems Engineering</i></strong>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </Collapse>

